      "type": "line-break"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "極常用的Git 上傳 cheet sheet"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "listType": "ordered",
      "items": [
        "`git init` → 初始化本地 repo",
        "`git status` → 檢視當前變更",
        "`git add .` / `git add <file>` → 暫存變更",
        "`git commit -m \"feat: init project\"` → 建立提交",
        "`git push -u origin main` → 首次推送並綁定上游",
        "`git pull` → 拉取遠端更新（與本地合併）"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-break"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "content": "額外嘅 Git 指令"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "listType": "ordered",
      "items": [
        "`git branch -M main` → 設定分支",
        "`git checkout {branchName}` → 切換分支",
        "`git remote add origin <repo_url>` → 連結 GitHub",
        "`git push -u origin main` → 推送到遠端(指定遠端repo main branch)",
        "`git pull` → 拉取遠端更新"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "horizontal-rule"
